&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span&gt;you are committed to providing outstanding care for women and have a strong desire to provide the best birth possible but need a more flexible working option the Maternity department at Frimley Health is the perfect place.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for versatile and highly motivated Bank Midwives with a passion for ensuring every woman, baby and their family leaves our service having received a highly quality experience. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Joining our team of bank Midwives you will be providing a full range of care 24/7 across all hospital settings in state of the art facilities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;As part of our temporary staffing service you will maintain a good work/life balance, whilst having access to a range of employee benefits and training/study day opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
